      "name": "Steady-state RH index comparison against FDA benchmark experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) compared against experimental measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump test rig at 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean RH prediction error is 8.3% across all conditions. Validation performed exclusively under steady-state, Newtonian blood viscosity assumptions matching the model configuration. No operating point with pulsatile or non-Newtonian conditions was included in the validation matrix."
    },
