      "rationale": "Experimental conditions span 3–6 L/min and 2000–3500 RPM, covering the clinical CPB operating envelope. Fluid temperature held at 37°C ± 0.5°C. Bovine blood with measured hematocrit 35 ± 2% used. Conditions are adequately representative of the COU for MRL 2."
    },
