      "rationale": "RH index percent error ranges from 2.1% to 14.6% across 5 operating points; mean error 8.3%. All predictions fall within experimental measurement uncertainty bounds (±15%). Comparison is deemed adequate for MRL 2 decision support. No comparison of local shear stress distributions or transient flow features was performed."
